  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: c513d81420ae4244ea5fa86c11a4a29b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Completed_Dialog
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogData
  lines:
  - At last. It is done. Your assistance has been vital for our experiments.
  - I hope you have learnt a thing or too alongside our robot. This information is
    extremely relevant for the future, you never know, it may too help you one day.
  - As a parting gift and as a statement of our appreciation, take this golden medal.
  - If I recall you now have all three? Bronze, Silver and Gold?
  - I am sure there was someone in the forest you could talk to who would be willing
    to exchange an expert medal for all of them...
